    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.72)) * wp.sin(tmp))
    tmp = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.02 + v2 + 0.69)) + wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.25)))
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.13 - v2 + 0.42)) + v1)
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.75)) - wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.89)))
    v2 = (tmp - 0.75)
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.cos(v2 + 0.18) + (tmp + 0.28 + v2 + 0.07)))
    v2 = (((v0 + 0.53 + v2 + 0.09) - wp.abs(v1 + 0.32)) * wp.abs(v0))
    data[tid] = v0
